 2020 '''Moto2 World Championship''' is a part of the 72nd [[F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Motocyclisme|F.I.M.]] [[Road racing|Road Racing]] World Championship season.\n\n==Teams and riders==\n{|\n|\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\"\n|-\n!Team\n!Constructor\n!Motorcycle\n!{{Tooltip|No.|Bike number}}\n!Rider\n!Rounds\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{flagicon|USA}} American Racing \n! rowspan=\"23\" | [[Kalex]]\n|rowspan=\"23\"| Moto2\n|align=center| 16\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Joe Roberts (motorcyclist)|Joe Roberts]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=center| 42\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Marcos Ram\u00edrez (motorcyclist)|Marcos Ram\u00edrez]]\n| 1\n|-\n|rowspan=2| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Marc VDS Racing Team|EG 0,0 Marc VDS]]\n|align=center| 22\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Sam Lowes]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.motogp.com/en/news/2019/09/06/sam-lowes-joins-team-estrella-galicia-0-0-marc-vds-for-2020/307233|title=Sam Lowes joins Team Estrella Galicia 0,0 Marc VDS for 2020|accessdate= 6 September 2019|work=MotoGP.com|publisher=[[Dorna Sports]]}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n|align=center| 37\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Augusto Fern\u00e1ndez (motorcyclist)|Augusto Fern\u00e1ndez]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crash.net/motogp/news/934618/1/moto2-fernandez-takes-marquez-s-spot-marc-vds|title=Moto2: Fernandez takes Marquez\u2019s spot at Marc VDS|first=Haydn|last=Cobb|date=24 November 2019|website=Crash.net|language=en|access-date=24 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n|rowspan=2| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Gresini Racing|Federal Oil Gresini Moto2]]\n|align=center| 11\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Nicol\u00f2 Bulega]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=center|57\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Edgar Pons]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crash.net/motogp/news/933603/1/moto2-pons-joins-bulega-gresini|title=Pons joins Bulega at Gresini|date=11 November 2019|website=Crash|language=en|access-date=13 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n|rowspan=2| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Pons Racing|Flexbox HP40]] \n|align=center| 7\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Lorenzo Baldassarri]]<ref